snippet.title: The Eye Of Typhoon (3DO)
snippet.description: Developed by Viccom, this is a rare game released only in South Korea that was originally slated for the Neo Geo, but only came out for 3DO and PC. This is recorded from actual 3DO console running sVideo into a capture device from an upscaler which has left some motion artifacts. No emulation! It gets pretty tough after the first couple fights.
